<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki ʋt, 'ho minti;
 Et pim ahanchi fehnʋshke;
 'Chin Chihowa sia hoke;
 Hʋs sa haiyaklo pullashke.

[V2]
 Yakni achukma fehna kʋt
 Ilʋppa talaia hoke;
 Aiokcha̱ya fehna yoke;
 Hʋsh holitobli pullashke.

[V3]
 Sa shakba pohloma hoka
 Hʋsh foyuka pullakbano;
 Hʋchim ahni li fehnʋshke;
 Hʋs sa̱ yihi̱mmi pullashke.</lyrics>
<aka>God inviting sinners.</aka>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Ʋba Pi̱ki ʋt, 'Ho minti' ƲIT6</title>
<hymn_number>6</hymn_number>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
</song>